## 主机信息查询
1. QHostInfo类的使用 *还有一个QNetworkInterface类，我感觉用处不大，就不写了*  

|QHostInfo类|功能|
|----|----|
|QString hostname = QHostInfo::localHostName();|本地主机名|
|QHostInfo hostinfo = QHostInfo::fromName(hostname);|本机的IP地址|
|QList<QHostAddress> addList = hostinfo.addresses();|IP地址列表|
|QHostAddress aHost = addList.at(i);aHost.protocol() == QAbstractSocket::IPv4Protocol|判断是不是IP地址类型的|
|QHostInfo::lookupHost(hostname,this,SLOT(FunLookedUpHostInfo(QHostInfo)));|以异步方式根据主机名查找主机的IP地址，并返回一个表示本次查找的ID|

```
tcpcode::tcpcode(QWidget *parent)
    : QMainWindow(parent)
    , ui(new Ui::tcpcode)
{
ui->setupUi(this);
flag_ready = false;
tcpserver = new QTcpServer(this);  //类指针是需要开辟空间的
tcpsocket = new QTcpSocket(this);
tcpClient = new QTcpSocket(this);

//服务器绑定的槽函数
//这里绑定的信号是 发现新客户端接入时发射的信号 
connect(tcpserver,SIGNAL(newConnection()),this,SLOT(funonNewConnection()));

//客户端要绑定的槽函数
connect(tcpClient,SIGNAL(connected()),this,SLOT(ConConnected()));
connect(tcpClient,SIGNAL(disconnected()),this,SLOT(ConDisconnected()));
connect(tcpClient,SIGNAL(stateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)),this,SLOT(ConSocketStateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)));
connect(tcpClient,SIGNAL(readyRead()),this,SLOT(ConSocketReadyRead()));
//初始化全部禁止
ui->btn_startlisten->setEnabled(0);
ui->btn_stoplisten->setEnabled(0);
ui->btn_linkserver->setEnabled(0);
ui->btn_breaklink->setEnabled(0);
ui->Edit_listenport->setEnabled(0);
ui->Edit_listenip->setEnabled(0);
ui->Edit_serverip->setEnabled(0);
ui->Edit_serverport->setEnabled(0);
}

tcpcode::~tcpcode()
{
    delete tcpClient;
    delete tcpsocket;
    delete tcpserver;
    delete ui;
}

//newConnection() 绑定的槽函数    
void tcpcode::funonNewConnection()
{
    tcpsocket = tcpserver->nextPendingConnection();  //获取一个QTcpSocket类型的对象
    //QTcpSocket对象信号与槽函数绑定，和客户端通讯还是依靠QTcpSocket对象
    connect(tcpsocket,SIGNAL(connected()),this,SLOT(onClientConnected()));   
    connect(tcpsocket,SIGNAL(disconnected()),this,SLOT(onClientDisconnected()));
    connect(tcpsocket,SIGNAL(stateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)),
                 this,SLOT(onSocketStateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)));
    connect(tcpsocket,SIGNAL(readyRead()),this,SLOT(onSocketReadyRead()));

}


//发送信息的函数   客户端和服务端公用一个
void tcpcode::on_btn_sendmessage_clicked()
{
    QString msg = ui->Edit_message->text();
    ui->Edit_message->clear();
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("[发送] "+msg);
    QByteArray str = msg.toUtf8();
    str.append("\n");
    if(ui->isClient->isChecked())
    {
        tcpClient->write(str);
    }

    if(ui->isServer->isChecked())
    {
        tcpsocket->write(str);
    }
}

//============================服务端=============================
//==============================================================
void tcpcode::on_btn_startlisten_clicked()  //开始监听按键
{
   if(ui->isServer->isChecked() == 0)
   {
       QMessageBox::warning(this,"注意","没有选择是服务端还是客户端","确定","取消");
       return;
   }
   if(ui->Edit_listenip->text().isEmpty() || ui->Edit_listenport->text().isEmpty())
   {
       QMessageBox::warning(this,"注意","IP地址和端口不能为空","确定","取消");
       return;
   }

   QString  IP  = ui->Edit_listenip->text();                  //监听
   quint16  Port= (ui->Edit_listenport->text()).toUShort();   //获取IP和端口

   QHostAddress addr(IP);
   tcpserver->listen(addr,Port);

  if((tcpserver->serverAddress().toString()).isEmpty() || (QString::number(tcpserver->serverPort()) == 0))
  {//数据没有填写就返回继续等待
     return ;
  }

    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**开始监听**");
   ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**服务器地址: "+tcpserver->serverAddress().toString());
   ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**服务器端口: "+QString::number(tcpserver->serverPort()));

   ui->btn_startlisten->setEnabled(0);
   ui->Edit_listenip->setEnabled(0);
   ui->Edit_listenport->setEnabled(0);
   ui->btn_stoplisten->setEnabled(1);
}

void tcpcode::on_btn_stoplisten_clicked()   //停止监听
{
    if(tcpserver->isListening())
    {
        tcpserver->close();
        ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**监听已经停止**");
    }
    ui->btn_startlisten->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_listenip->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_listenport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_stoplisten->setEnabled(0);
}

//下面4个是QTcpSocket对象信号绑定的槽函数
void tcpcode::onClientConnected()
{
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**客户端已经连接");
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**客户端地址 = "+tcpsocket->peerAddress().toString());
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**客户端端口 = "+QString::number(tcpsocket->peerPort()));
}
void tcpcode::onClientDisconnected()
{
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**客户端断开连接");
    tcpsocket->deleteLater();
}
void tcpcode::onSocketStateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState socketState)
{
    switch(socketState)
    {
      case  QAbstractSocket::UnconnectedState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("UnconnectedState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::HostLookupState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("HostLookupState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ConnectingState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ConnectingState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ConnectedState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ConnectedState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::BoundState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("BoundState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ClosingState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ClosingState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ListeningState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ListeningState"); break;
    }
}
void tcpcode::onSocketReadyRead()
{
    while(tcpsocket->canReadLine())
    {
        ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("[接收] "+tcpsocket->readLine()+"\n");
    }
}





//============================客户端=============================

void tcpcode::on_btn_linkserver_clicked()//连接到服务器
{
    if(ui->isClient->isChecked() == 0)
    {
        QMessageBox::warning(this,"注意","没有选择是服务端还是客户端","确定","取消");
        return;
    }
    if(ui->Edit_serverip->text().isEmpty() || ui->Edit_serverport->text().isEmpty())
    {
        QMessageBox::warning(this,"注意","IP地址和端口不能为空","确定","取消");
        return;
    }

    QString addr = ui->Edit_serverip->text();
    quint16 port = (ui->Edit_serverport->text()).toUShort();
    tcpClient->connectToHost(addr,port);                        //连接到服务端

    ui->btn_breaklink->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_linkserver->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_serverport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_serverport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("开始连接服务器");

}

void tcpcode::on_btn_breaklink_clicked()//与服务器断开连接
{
    if(tcpClient->state() == QAbstractSocket::ConnectedState)
    {
        tcpClient->disconnectFromHost();
    }
    ui->btn_breaklink->setEnabled(0);
    ui->btn_linkserver->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_serverport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_serverport->setEnabled(1);
}

void tcpcode::ConConnected()
{
     ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**已经连接到服务器");
}

void tcpcode::ConDisconnected()
{
     ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("**已与服务器断开连接");

void tcpcode::ConSocketStateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState socketState)
{
    switch(socketState)
    {
      case  QAbstractSocket::UnconnectedState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("UnconnectedState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::HostLookupState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("HostLookupState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ConnectingState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ConnectingState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ConnectedState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ConnectedState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::BoundState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("BoundState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ClosingState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ClosingState"); break;
      case  QAbstractSocket::ListeningState:
      ui->textBrowser_showmessage->append("ListeningState"); break;
    }
}

{
    while(tcpClient->canReadLine())
```

## QUdpSocket 实现 UDP通信

&emsp;&emsp;需要用到的函数
|函数|功能|
|----|----|
|bind|为UDP通信绑定一个端口|
|abort|解除绑定|
|writeDatagram|向目标地址和端口的UDP客户端发送数据报|
|hasPendingDatagram|当至少有一个数据报需要读取时|
|pendingDatagramSize|返回第一个带读取的数据报的大小|
|readDatagram|读取第一个数据报，返回成功读取的数据报的字节数|
|joinMulticastGroup|加入一个多播组|
|leaveMulticastGroup|离开一个多播组|

<br/>  

```
例程代码

#include "socketmainwindow.h"
#include "ui_socketmainwindow.h"

SocketMainWindow::SocketMainWindow(QWidget *parent)
    : QMainWindow(parent)
    , ui(new Ui::SocketMainWindow)
{
    ui->setupUi(this);
    udpsocket = new QUdpSocket(this);
    connect(udpsocket,SIGNAL(readyRead()),this,SLOT(UdpSocketReadData()));
    connect(udpsocket,SIGNAL(stateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)),this,SLOT(onSocketStateChange(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)));
}

SocketMainWindow::~SocketMainWindow()
{
    delete ui;
    delete udpsocket;
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_Btn_bind_clicked()
{
    QString bindport = ui->Edit_bindport->text();
    quint16 portnum  = bindport.toUShort();
    if(udpsocket->bind(portnum))
    {
        ui->Bro_msg->append("绑定成功");
        ui->Bro_msg->append("=================");
    }
    else
    {
        ui->Bro_msg->append("绑定失败");
    }
    ui->Btn_bind->setEnabled(0);
    ui->btn_unbind->setEnabled(1);
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_btn_unbind_clicked()
{
    udpsocket->abort();
    ui->Bro_msg->append("已经解除绑定");
    ui->Bro_msg->append("=================");
    ui->Btn_bind->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_unbind->setEnabled(0);
}


void SocketMainWindow::on_btn_send_clicked()
{
    QString msg = ui->Edit_SendMsg->text();
    QByteArray str = msg.toUtf8();

    QString targetIP = ui->Edit_targetip->text();
    QString targetPort = ui->Edit_targetport->text();

    QHostAddress targetAddr(targetIP);
    quint16 targetnum  = targetPort.toUShort();

    udpsocket->writeDatagram(str,targetAddr,targetnum);

    ui->Bro_msg->append("[发送消息] "+msg);

}

void SocketMainWindow::on_btn_broadcastsend_clicked()
{
    QString msg = ui->Edit_SendMsg->text();
    QByteArray str = msg.toUtf8();

    QString targetPort = ui->Edit_targetport->text();

    quint16 targetnum  = targetPort.toUShort();

    udpsocket->writeDatagram(str,QHostAddress::Broadcast,targetnum);

    ui->Bro_msg->append("[发送消息] "+msg);
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_btn_multicastsend_clicked()
{
    QString msg = ui->Edit_SendMsg->text();
    QByteArray str = msg.toUtf8();

    QString Port = ui->Edit_multicastport->text();
    quint16 Portnum  = Port.toUShort();

    udpsocket->writeDatagram(str,groupAddress,Portnum);
    ui->Bro_msg->append("[发送消息] "+msg);
}


void SocketMainWindow::UdpSocketReadData()
{
   while(udpsocket->hasPendingDatagrams())
   {
       QByteArray datagram;
       datagram.resize(udpsocket->pendingDatagramSize());

       QHostAddress peerAddr;
       udpsocket->readDatagram(datagram.data(),datagram.size());

       QString msg = datagram.data();

       ui->Bro_msg->append("[接收消息] "+msg);
   }
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_Btn_joinmulticast_clicked()
{
    QString MulticastIP    = ui->Edit_multicastip->text();
    groupAddress = QHostAddress(MulticastIP);
    QString MulticastPort  = ui->Edit_multicastport->text();
    quint16 PortNum  = MulticastPort.toUShort();
    if(udpsocket->bind(QHostAddress::AnyIPv4,PortNum,QUdpSocket::ShareAddress))
    {
        udpsocket->joinMulticastGroup(groupAddress);
        ui->Bro_msg->append("加入组播成功");
        ui->Bro_msg->append("<<组播地址>> "+ MulticastIP);
        ui->Bro_msg->append("<<组播端口>> "+ MulticastPort);
    }
    else
    {
         ui->Bro_msg->append("加入组播失败");
    }
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_Btn_quitmulticast_clicked()
{
    udpsocket->leaveMulticastGroup(groupAddress);
    udpsocket->abort();
    ui->Bro_msg->append("已经退出组播，解除端口绑定");
}

void SocketMainWindow::on_rbtn_signalcast_clicked()
{
    //单播
    ui->btn_send->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Btn_bind->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_unbind->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_bindport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_targetip->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_targetport->setEnabled(1);

    //多播
    ui->Edit_multicastip->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_multicastport->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_joinmulticast->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_quitmulticast->setEnabled(0);
    ui->btn_multicastsend->setEnabled(0);

    //广播
    ui->btn_broadcastsend->setEnabled(0);


}

void SocketMainWindow::on_rbtn_multicast_clicked()
{

    //单播
    ui->btn_send->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_bind->setEnabled(0);
    ui->btn_unbind->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_bindport->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_targetip->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_targetport->setEnabled(0);

    //多播
    ui->Edit_multicastip->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_multicastport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Btn_joinmulticast->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Btn_quitmulticast->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_multicastsend->setEnabled(1);

    //广播
    ui->btn_broadcastsend->setEnabled(0);

void SocketMainWindow::on_rbtn_broadcast_clicked()
{
    //单播
    ui->btn_send->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_bind->setEnabled(1);
    ui->btn_unbind->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_bindport->setEnabled(1);
    ui->Edit_targetip->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_targetport->setEnabled(1);

    //多播
    ui->Edit_multicastip->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Edit_multicastport->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_joinmulticast->setEnabled(0);
    ui->Btn_quitmulticast->setEnabled(0);
    ui->btn_multicastsend->setEnabled(0);

    //广播
    ui->btn_broadcastsend->setEnabled(1);
}


void SocketMainWindow::onSocketStateChange(QAbstractSocket::SocketState state)
{
    switch(state)
    {
      case QAbstractSocket::UnconnectedState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***未连接状态***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::HostLookupState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***正在执行查找主机名***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::ConnectingState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***正在建立连接***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::ConnectedState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***已经建立连接***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::BoundState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***绑定到一个地址和端口***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::ClosingState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***套接字即将关闭***");
        break;
      case QAbstractSocket::ListeningState:
        ui->Bro_msg->append("***监听状态***");
        break;
    }
}
```  

### 使用Udp组播时遇到的问题
&emsp;&emsp;遇到了两台电脑在同一个局域网下不能使用组播的情况，解决方法就是把虚拟机网卡关了然后在网络协议中加入多播协议


### 单播、组播、广播模式的异同
&emsp;&emsp;比较要素单播广播组播要绑定的目标地址根据另一台机器的地址和而定地址255.255.255.255有共同约定好的组播IP地址接收数据的函数三个都一样绑定函数和解绑定函数两个基本一样就是地址不同而已除了绑定和解绑定函数需要加入组播地址和退出组播

### 套接字的状态描述
&emsp;&emsp;只需要在界面的构造函数里面将信号和函数绑定即可，状态改变时会触发
```
 connect(udpsocket,SIGNAL(stateChanged(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)),this,SLOT(onSocketStateChange(QAbstractSocket::SocketState)));
```  

|Constant|Value|Description|翻译|
|----|----|----|----|
|UnconnectedState|0|The socket is not connected|没连接|
|HostLookupState|1|The socket is performing a host name lookup|套接字正在执行主机名查找|
|ConnectingState|2|The socket has started establishing a connection.|套接字已开始建立连接。|
|ConnectedState|3|A connection is established.|建立连接。|
|BoundState|4|The socket is bound to an address and port.|套接字绑定到一个地址和端口。|
|ClosingState|6|The socket is about to close (data may still be waiting to be written).|套接字即将关闭(数据可能仍在等待写入)。|
|ListeningState|5|For internal use only.|仅供内部使用。(这不是监听状态吗)|
